  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Otosclerosis where surgery is planned

          -  Air / bone gap larger than 20 dB

          -  Normal middle ear status

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Hypersensitivity to acetylcysteine

          -  Deafness on the other ear

          -  Stapedotomy previously performed on the ear

          -  Pregnancy

          -  Asthma
      </textblock>
